/span></p>","frontmatter":{"title":"2022技育展に登壇した話","date":"September 16, 2022","description":"2022技育展において、テーマ「世の中を楽しくする」に登壇しました。"}},"previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/new-beginnings/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"New Beginnings"}},"next":null},"pageContext":{"id":"fff6694a-867d-53f9-b8c4-55603496da07","previousPostId":"75484a84-a070-5570-b37f-7354d83f4b81","nextPostId":null}},"staticQueryHashes":["2841359383","3257411868"]}